{"_path":"/construction/c08","_dir":"construction","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"南亞科技南林科技園區建廠","description":null,"image":"/images/construction/c08-1.jpeg","sequence":8,"category":"工商發展","status":"2.施工","type":"green","budget":"3,000億","link":null,"head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2025-12-31T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"南亞科技南林科技園區建廠"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"南亞科技南林科技園區建廠"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"計畫概要"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"計畫概要"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"項目 南亞科技南林科技園區建廠"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"類別 工商發展 - CON-08"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"完工 2025"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"經費 3,000 億"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"狀態 施工"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"建設詳情"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"建設詳情"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"南林科技園區\n台塑集團旗下的 DRAM 製造商南亞科技落腳新北市泰山區南林科技園區，廠商投資三千億元，興建十奈米十二吋先進晶圓新廠，全案預計二 ○ 二五年完工，開發土地面積約十二．○ 三公頃，每年可創造超過七百億元產值，並提供三千個就業機會。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"南亞科技投資興建雙層無塵先進晶圓廠，開發土地面積約十二．○ 三公頃，分為 A 到 D 四區建築基地，總開發量體達十一萬六八四九坪，包含 A 區主廠房、B 區水資源再生中心、C 區清水廠的停車場及 D 區研發大樓，未來七年分三階段擴增產能規模，預估完工後開始裝機投片量產。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"泰山&龜山的地理位置正好位於大台北地區中心點，由南亞科技公司、南亞塑膠公司結合鄰近的明志科技大學，培育專業技術人才，形成半導體產業聚落，不但活絡地方經濟，更可發揮強大的磁吸效應，吸引 IC 產業上、下游供應鏈廠商進駐，帶動整體地方產業發展與升級。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"相關資訊\n自由時報 2022/06/28 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/NewTaipei/paper/1525407"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"南亞科技建新廠每年將創 7 百億產值"}]},{"type":"text","value":"\nYoutube 2022/06/23 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M0qma7tL0ms"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":" 南亞科 3 千億建新廠"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c08-1.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c08-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"南亞科技南林科技園區建廠","depth":2,"text":"南亞科技南林科技園區建廠","children":[{"id":"計畫概要","depth":3,"text":"計畫概要"},{"id":"建設詳情","depth":3,"text":"建設詳情"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:construction:c08.md","_source":"content","_file":"construction/c08.md","_extension":"md"}